# Forgetful Doodle 2.0 — environment variables

# Claude API key for AI deck generation (Claude Sonnet 5), used server-side only
# by the /api/generate proxy. Without it, AI deck-making is disabled and you can
# still hand-build decks; the app runs fine locally without a key.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Vercel Postgres connection string. Set automatically when you link a Vercel
# Postgres store to the project. Without it, best scores / streak / decks fall
# back to browser localStorage (per-device). Provide one for cross-device sync.
POSTGRES_URL=
